    { "type": "text", "id": "steam_title", "x": 68, "y": 613, "width": 179, "height": 18,
      "text": "SteamScraper",
      "originalText": "SteamScraper",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 512, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 513, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "steam_body", "x": 68, "y": 633, "width": 179, "height": 180,
      "text": "search(name)\n  1. storesearch API\n  2. appdetails API\n  → price_overview\n\nscrape()\n  → featuredcategories\n    top_sellers\n\nRegion: CO (COP)\nCurrency: native COP\nFuzzy: difflib 0.4",
      "originalText": "search(name)\n  1. storesearch API\n  2. appdetails API\n  → price_overview\n\nscrape()\n  → featuredcategories\n    top_sellers\n\nRegion: CO (COP)\nCurrency: native COP\nFuzzy: difflib 0.4",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 514, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 515, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.5 },

    { "type": "rectangle", "id": "epic_box", "x": 265, "y": 604, "width": 195, "height": 215,
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "#93c5fd", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 520, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 521, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": [], "link": null, "locked": false, "roundness": {"type": 3} },
    { "type": "text", "id": "epic_title", "x": 273, "y": 613, "width": 179, "height": 18,
      "text": "EpicScraper",
      "originalText": "EpicScraper",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 522, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 523, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "epic_body", "x": 273, "y": 633, "width": 179, "height": 180,
      "text": "search(name)\n  epicstore_api lib\n  fetch_store_games()\n  → fuzzy match 0.4\n  → normalize unicode\n\nscrape()\n  → not implemented\n  returns []\n\nURL: productSlug\n  or pageSlug\n  or urlSlug\nFuzzy: difflib 0.4",
      "originalText": "search(name)\n  epicstore_api lib\n  fetch_store_games()\n  → fuzzy match 0.4\n  → normalize unicode\n\nscrape()\n  → not implemented\n  returns []\n\nURL: productSlug\n  or pageSlug\n  or urlSlug\nFuzzy: difflib 0.4",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 524, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 525, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.5 },

    { "type": "rectangle", "id": "gog_box", "x": 470, "y": 604, "width": 200, "height": 215,
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "#93c5fd", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 530, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 531, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": [], "link": null, "locked": false, "roundness": {"type": 3} },
    { "type": "text", "id": "gog_title", "x": 478, "y": 613, "width": 184, "height": 18,
      "text": "GogScraper",
      "originalText": "GogScraper",
      "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 532, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 533, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.25 },
    { "type": "text", "id": "gog_body", "x": 478, "y": 633, "width": 184, "height": 180,
      "text": "search(name)\n  3 fallback APIs:\n  1. catalog.gog.com\n  2. www.gog.com/ajax\n  3. embed.gog.com\n\nscrape()\n  → catalog ?order=\n    trending&limit=50\n\nUSD→COP exchange\ncurrencyExchange.py\nFuzzy: 0.4, +0.8 boost\n  if term in title",
      "originalText": "search(name)\n  3 fallback APIs:\n  1. catalog.gog.com\n  2. www.gog.com/ajax\n  3. embed.gog.com\n\nscrape()\n  → catalog ?order=\n    trending&limit=50\n\nUSD→COP exchange\ncurrencyExchange.py\nFuzzy: 0.4, +0.8 boost\n  if term in title",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#1e3a5f", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "angle": 0,
      "seed": 534, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 535, "isDeleted": false, "groupIds": [],
      "boundElements": null, "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null, "lineHeight": 1.5 },

