      "text": "search(name)\n  1. autosuggest API\n     → ProductIDs\n  2. products details\n     → PC filter\n  → DisplaySkuAvail..\n    .Price (MSRP+List)\n\nscrape()\n  → not implemented\n  returns []\n\nMarket: CO es-CO\nFuzzy: difflib 0.4",
