    { "type": "text", "id": "ext_rabbitmq_t", "x": 928, "y": 877, "width": 334, "height": 100,
      "text": "RabbitMQ 3  (game_prices_queue)\nAMQP :5672  ·  Management UI :15672\n\nDurable queue — messages persist on restart\nDelivery mode 2 — persistent messages\n\nConsumed by: gateway-service\n  → priceUpdateBus → SSE to browser",
      "originalText": "RabbitMQ 3  (game_prices_queue)\nAMQP :5672  ·  Management UI :15672\n\nDurable queue — messages persist on restart\nDelivery mode 2 — persistent messages\n\nConsumed by: gateway-service\n  → priceUpdateBus → SSE to browser",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 3, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
